    "text": "I've considered making a drag and drop JSON viewer and editor, that you can just plug APIs into, and then create functionality and views around. So for example, make it easy to get at the data in existing things like FaceBook or your bank account, and combine and interact with or however you want. Maybe something like that could be a good bridge from existing infrastructure, into something like what you're building",
